{"tid":886983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父遭警箍頸後亡 長女：李家超盧偉聰「不幸」論在傷口灑鹽 家屬難受","createTime":"2018-11-02T13:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T14:26:05.000Z","uid":92301,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"34861084530a89e45fd2c9a36e5b5d913ea8aca7","tid":886983,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"的士司機陳輝旺被警員箍頸致頸椎移位，最終不治，死因庭裁定他非法被殺，警務處長盧偉聰、保安局長李家超先後以「不幸」來形容事件，未有道歉，建制派議員梁美芬更稱事件可能影響警隊士氣。死者長女陳盈康今日通過朋友回應《立場新聞》指，接連的「不幸」評論令家屬非常難受，希望不要再在傷口灑鹽。<br />\n<br />\n陳盈康又表示，法庭裁定父親「非法被殺」，「是一個毫無合理疑點的『誤殺』判決」，促請律政司盡快跟進、正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E7%88%B6%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E7%AE%8D%E9%A0%B8%E5%BE%8C%E4%BA%A1-%E9%95%B7%E5%A5%B3-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B8-%E8%AB%96%E5%9C%A8%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%A3%E7%81%91%E9%B9%BD-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E9%9B%A3%E5%8F%97/?fbclid=IwAR1qlLpFuNT2GKxNkTxoN-JS7nDaVw_Om6WDEItyaunCNcb00G2MU1hkHkQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2588%25B6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25AE%258D%25E9%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B9%25B8-%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%2581%2591%25E9%25B9%25BD-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%258F%2597%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1qlLpFuNT2GKxNkTxoN-JS7nDaVw_Om6WDEItyaunCNcb00G2MU1hkHkQ&d=XjQgjJGG3Jmbsj%2FlSM8MSJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9acec5fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2588%25B6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25AE%258D%25E9%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B9%25B8-%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2582%25B7%25